 provide strategic advice best practices bestinclass capabilities and execution to support either brand or corporate teams functions include global communications legal consumer insights finance global supply chain research and development human resources and many others apply for a job new applicants search our database for open positions find the job thats right for you search all jobs returning applicants if youve already created an account please log in to return to your existing profile return to application hiring faqs to what job level should i apply entrylevel positions include administrative assistant coordinator administrator designer and associate midlevel positions include assistant manager manager senior designer associate design director director and executive director seniorlevel positions include vice president senior vice president general manager and president how do i apply to a brand retail and field sales position please visit our individual brand websites to review and apply for open positions please note that many of our retail positions are filled by the department store which makes all final hiring decisions what are the next steps after i apply to a position should i follow up our goal is to personally respond to each application however we ask that you be patient as we review all applications candidates will be selected and contacted on the basis of the qualifications of their applications while we encourage you to continually review our current openings your information will be retained to ensure that you are considered for future opportunities are there temporary positions available we have a variety of temporary support assignments that range across all brands and departments and vary in length from a oneday assignment to a shortterm project do you have any undergraduate or graduate rotational programs yes in north america we do learn more about our presidential associate undergraduate and presidential management associate programs graduate do you offer internship opportunities yes we offer a formal internship experience lauder summer internship program in the us for undergraduate and graduate students additionally our global locations offer internship opportunities based on business needs enrollment for summer  internship opportunities will begin in september  we are an equal opportunity employer we are an equal opportunity employer and provide all employees and applicants for employment with equal employment opportunities we embrace the uniqueness of each individual and are committed to identifying developing and maximizing individual talents we provide all employees and applicants for employment with equal employment opportunities without regard to race creed color religion gender age national origin alienage or citizenship status sexual orientation gender identity or expression marital partnership or familial status disability genetic information veteranmilitary status domestic violence victim status or any other characteristic protected by law the company will provide reasonable accommodation consistent with the law to otherwise qualified employees and prospective employees with a disability and to employees and prospective employees with needs related to their religious observance or practices you may also like our business of beauty working here careers invent craft accelerate create amplify connect who we areour brandsour commitmentstalentnews  mediainvestorssuppliers connect with usfacebookinstagramlinkedin contact us privacy policy site map terms and conditions copyright   share this article the estée lauder companies apply video text only who we are – the estée lauder companies inc who we are we are currently going under maintenance untill  am est for meanwhile please visit us at facebook and linkedin skip to main content who we are leadership executive leadershipboard of directors the lauder family the estée storya family in business global reach global operationsretail experiencestrav