fit candidates who successfully match the profile of what we’re looking for in the role will be invited to interview either by phone or in person interviews are conducted by human resources hiring managers and leaders our interview style consists of behavioral interviews that assess core competencies and cultural fit how can i be informed of new openings in my area of interest we encourage candidates to create a personal profile on the estée lauder companies job sites within that profile you are able to designate the areas of interest or specific functions where you would be interested in working when new roles become available that match your preferences our job posting system will automatically notify you investing in our company who owns the estée lauder companies the estée lauder companies is a publiclytraded family controlled company what is the stock symbol for the estée lauder companies inc class a common stock and what stock exchange is the company listed on the stock symbol is el and it is listed on the new york stock exchange when was the estée lauder companies’ initial public offering and at what price did it go public the company went public on november   at a price of  per share equal to  adjusted for stock splits what are the estée lauder companies’ earnings release dates for the coming year earnings release and conference call dates can be found in the events  presentations section on this site additionally archives of past earnings conference calls can also be accessed when is the next annual meeting of stockholders this information and more can be found on the events  presentations section on this site about our products how can i find out the ingredients of a product the ingredients in all of our products can be found on the packaging if you are unable to find the ingredient listing for your product contact us with the exact name and shade of the product you use or would be interested in using and we will send you the ingredient listing how can i f