 perfect world line of products origins is also notable for its ongoing collaboration with dr andrew weil in his own line of products that target inflammation and sensitive skin after  years the brand now has approximately  stores globally and plans to expand by opening around  stores in china on may   origins launched an interactive photo and video app on itunes called quarterlifecrisis that consumers can use to take stickerdecorated selfies with productsedit in november  origins launched the first organic line of skin care products to carry a  organic usda certification seal in february  origins launched happy birthdayplantscription an antiaging serum which claims to rival the leading antiwrinkle prescription retinoid creams with  irritation in june  origins launched a new skincare collection targeting the effects of global pollution called three part harmony this is in line with its global pollution defense campaign the brand has also announced a new original skin collection later this year to target younger consumers skin concerns with rough texture enlarged pores stressed skin and loss of brightness operations and financesedit origins projections for  include continued strong topline growth increasing investment spending constant currency net sales growth to be about  constant currency growth to be about  and emerging markets excluding china led by turkey brazil and south africa to rise nearly  at the end of the  fiscal year europe the middle east and africa represented  of net sales and  of operating income and asia and the pacific region represented  of net sales and  of operating income asiaedit chinaedit beginning july   estée lauder companies is set to lower prices on many of its most popular products in china affecting all skincare and makeup brands under the company and including origins estée lauder clinique la mer mac bobbi brown and lab series the price reduction varies from  on the bestselling la mer facial cream to  on an origins fragrance hong kong