 origins natural resources inc origins at dfs galleria customhouse in auckland new zealand type division of holding company estée lauder companies inc industry cosmetics founded  products skincare hair care makeup and fragrance parent estée lauder companies inc website wwworiginscom origins is a cosmetics brand from the us founded in  by leonard lauder son of estée lauder it is one of the original brands of the estée lauder companies contents  history  products  operations and finances  asia  china  hong kong  philippines  environmental commitment  breast cancer awareness campaign  feedback  references  external links historyedit the company is known for their natural skin care products notable lines include the a perfect world line of products origins is also notable for its ongoing collaboration with dr andrew weil in his own line of products that target inflammation and sensitive skin after  years the brand now has approximately  stores globally and plans to expand by opening around  stores in china on may   origins launched an interactive photo and video app on itunes called quarterlifecrisis that consumers can use to take stickerdecorated selfies with productsedit in november  origins launched the first organic line of skin care products to carry a  organic usda certification seal in february  origins launched happy birthdayplantscription an antiaging serum which claims to rival the leading antiwrinkle prescription retinoid creams with  irritation in june  origins launched a new skincare collection targeting the effects of global pollution called three part harmony this is in line with its global pollution defense campaign the brand has also announced a new original skin collection later this year to target younger consumers skin concerns with rough texture enlarged pores stressed skin and loss of brightness operations and financesedit origins projections for  include continued strong topline growth increasing investment spending constant currency net sales growth to be about  constant currency growth to be about  and emerging markets excluding china led by turkey brazil and south africa to rise nearly  at the end of the  fiscal year europe the middle east and africa represented  of net sales and  of operating income and asia and the pacific region represented  of net sales and  of operating income asiaedit chinaedit beginning july   estée lauder companies is set to lower prices on many of its most popular products in china affecting all skincare and makeup brands under the company and including origins estée lauder clinique la mer mac bobbi brown and lab series the price reduction varies from  on the bestselling la mer facial cream to  on an origins fragrance hong kongedit as of june   origins recently opened its first greenhouse concept store in the ifc mall in hong kong to envelop its customers in an immersive and personalized space the space showcases local material and artisanal work including a locally sourced granite communal stone stéphane de la faverie the senior vice president globalgeneral manager of origins ojon and darphin says that this concept retail store represents a major milestone for origins since its establishment  years ago philippinesedit origins first launched in the philippines in the early s as the sensory therapy peace of mind product grew in popularity a storeinstore is set to open in august  at sm makati after a year absence in the country and region except for hong kong environmental commitmentedit by age  origins has helped to plant over  trees breast cancer awareness campaignedit this section is empty you can help by adding to it july  feedbackedit olivia tong a research analyst and director of us cosmetics household and personal care at bank of america merrill lynch surveyed  millennial women between the ages of  and  using  brands to find out preferred cosmetics and beauty brands when asked what other important factors were not mentioned in their purchasing decisions many said naturals an